'''伊恩·西奧多爾·安德森'''（{{lang-en|Ian Theodore Anderson}}，{{bd|1998年|5月2日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前效力於亞特蘭大勇士。他是2016年大聯盟選秀的選秀探花。
==職業生涯==
===小聯盟===
安德森是2016年大聯盟選秀的探花，勇士隊和他以400萬美元簽約。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Braves tab prep right-hander Anderson at No. 3|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/183036526/braves-pick-pitcher-ian-anderson-in-mlb-draft?topicid=167757330|access-date=June 10, 2016|publisher=MLB.com|date=June 9, 2016|archive-date=2017-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170530034339/http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/183036526/braves-pick-pitcher-ian-anderson-in-mlb-draft/?topicid=167757330}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Bowman|first1=Mark|title=Braves agree with top Draft pick Anderson|url=http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/186153446/braves-agree-with-top-draft-pick-ian-anderson|access-date=June 26, 2016|publisher=MLB.com|date=June 25, 2016|archive-date=2016-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008154122/http://m.braves.mlb.com/news/article/186153446/braves-agree-with-top-draft-pick-ian-anderson/}}</ref>

安德森在小聯盟爬升的速度很快，2016年他從新人聯盟起步，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailygazette.com/news/2016/aug/05/anderson-promoted-class-ball/|title=Anderson promoted to Class A ball|work=The Daily Gazette|date=August 5, 2018|access-date=August 9, 2018|last1=Kelly|first1=Michael|archive-date=2016-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821040346/http://www.dailygazette.com/news/2016/aug/05/anderson-promoted-class-ball/}}</ref>2017年升上1A，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=666120#/career/R/pitching/2017/ALL|title=Ian Anderson Stats, Highlights, Bio – MiLB.com Stats – The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=MiLB.com|access-date=November 10, 2017|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129170103/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=666120#/career/R/pitching/2017/ALL}}</ref>2018年升上2A。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=666120#/career/R/pitching/2018/ALL|title=Ian Anderson Stats, Highlights, Bio – MiLB.com Stats – The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=MiLB.com|access-date=October 11, 2018|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129170103/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=666120#/career/R/pitching/2018/ALL}}</ref> 

2019年，安德森首度受邀參加大聯盟春訓。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Heneghan |first1=Kelsie |title=Braves invite four Top-100 prospects to camp |url=https://www.milb.com/milb/news/atlanta-braves-invite-four-top-100-prospects-to-major-league-spring-tr-303265540 |access-date=August 26, 2020 |publisher=MILB.com |date=January 28, 2019 |archive-date=2021-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303052314/https://www.milb.com/milb/news/atlanta-braves-invite-four-top-100-prospects-to-major-league-spring-tr-303265540 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Harris |first1=Chris |title=Mississippi Braves announce 2019 Opening Day roster |url=https://www.milb.com/news/gcs-305873318 |access-date=August 26, 2020 |publisher=MILB.com |date=April 2, 2019 |archive-date=2021-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303061539/https://www.milb.com/news/gcs-305873318 }}</ref>春訓結束後他回到2A，期間他還入選全明星未來之星賽。<ref>{{cite news |title=Six Mississippi Braves named to Southern League All-Star team |url=https://www.clarionledger.com/story/sports/m-braves/2019/06/06/mississippi-braves-baseball-southern-league-all-stars/1372268001/ |access-date=August 26, 2020 |work=Clarion Ledger |date=June 6, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Harris |first1=Chris |title=Cristian Pache and Ian Anderson named to All-Star Futures Game Roster |url=https://www.milb.com/mississippi/news/cristian-pache-and-ian-anderson-named-to-all-star-futures-game-roster-308575850 |access-date=August 26, 2020 |date=June 28, 2019 |archive-date=2021-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306052440/https://www.milb.com/mississippi/news/cristian-pache-and-ian-anderson-named-to-all-star-futures-game-roster-308575850 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/2019-futures-game-rosters?t=mlb-pipeline-coverage|title=Here are the 2019 Futures Game rosters|author=Jim Callis|website=MLB.com|date=June 28, 2019|access-date=June 28, 2019|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201083045/https://www.mlb.com/news/2019-futures-game-rosters?t=mlb-pipeline-coverage}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Schott |first1=Ken |title=Shenendehowa grad Anderson pitching in Futures Game |url=https://dailygazette.com/article/2019/07/05/shenendehowa-grad-anderson-pitching-in-futures-game |access-date=August 26, 2020 |work=The Daily Gazette |date=July 5, 2019 |archive-date=2019-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190706124935/https://dailygazette.com/article/2019/07/05/shenendehowa-grad-anderson-pitching-in-futures-game }}</ref>8月5日升上3A。<ref>{{cite news |title=Braves prospects Waters, Pache make Triple-A debuts |url=https://www.ajc.com/sports/braves-prospects-waters-pache-star-triple-debuts/1f6IpQAJCZdPyG6AJbEeEK/ |access-date=August 7, 2019 |work=Atlanta Journal Constitution |date=August 6, 2019 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227221143/https://www.ajc.com/sports/braves-prospects-waters-pache-star-triple-debuts/1f6IpQAJCZdPyG6AJbEeEK/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Dykstra |first1=Sam |title=Braves' Waters, Anderson promoted to Triple-A |url=https://www.milb.com/milb/news/atlanta-braves-drew-waters-ian-anderson-promoted-to-triple-a-gwinnett/c-309723648 |access-date=August 7, 2019 |publisher=MILB.com |date=August 5, 2019 |archive-date=2019-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807164649/https://www.milb.com/milb/news/atlanta-braves-drew-waters-ian-anderson-promoted-to-triple-a-gwinnett/c-309723648 }}</ref>
===大聯盟===
2020年，安德森受邀春訓。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Dykstra |first1=Sam |title=Braves' Waters, Anderson receive invites |url=https://www.milb.com/milb/news/atlanta-braves-drew-waters-ian-anderson-receive-spring-training-invite-312511332 |access-date=August 26, 2020 |publisher=MILB.com |date=January 22, 2020 |archive-date=2022-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412031833/https://www.milb.com/milb/news/atlanta-braves-drew-waters-ian-anderson-receive-spring-training-invite-312511332 }}</ref>不過由於春訓因為COVID-19疫情取消，因此勇士隊直接將安德森拉進60人名單內。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Maun |first1=Tyler |title=Top prospects named to 60-man player pools |url=https://www.milb.com/news/mlb-teams-announce-60-man-player-pools |access-date=August 26, 2020 |date=June 28, 2020 |archive-date=2021-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427143702/https://www.milb.com/news/mlb-teams-announce-60-man-player-pools }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Bowman |first1=Mark |title=Braves set player pool; 4 spots remain |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/braves-player-pool-for-2020 |access-date=August 26, 2020 |publisher=MLB.com |date=June 28, 2020 |archive-date=2020-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717192905/https://www.mlb.com/news/braves-player-pool-for-2020 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Burns |first1=Gabriel |title=Braves announce initial player pool for 2020 season |url=https://www.ajc.com/sports/baseball/braves-announce-initial-player-pool-for-2020-season/GniSFHCeJagawSBcEUDCWO/ |access-date=August 26, 2020 |work=Atlanta Journal Constitution |date=June 29, 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128010206/https://www.ajc.com/sports/baseball/braves-announce-initial-player-pool-for-2020-season/GniSFHCeJagawSBcEUDCWO/ }}</ref>8月26日，安德森成功登上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bowman |first1=Mark |title=Acuña, Markakis back; Anderson to debut |url=https://www.mlb.com/braves/news/ronald-acuna-activated-ian-anderson-called-up-by-braves |access-date=August 25, 2020 |publisher=MLB.com |date=August 25, 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123090209/https://www.mlb.com/braves/news/ronald-acuna-activated-ian-anderson-called-up-by-braves }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Ronald Acuna Jr., Nick Markakis return to Braves lineup; Ian Anderson promoted for MLB debut |url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/29738426/ronald-acuna-jr-nick-markakis-return-braves-lineup-ian-anderson-promoted-mlb-debut |access-date=August 25, 2020 |publisher=ESPN |date=August 25, 2020 |archive-date=2021-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201082336/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/29738426/ronald-acuna-jr-nick-markakis-return-braves-lineup-ian-anderson-promoted-mlb-debut }}</ref>他在初登板面對洋基隊一度投出5.1局無安打。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Burns |first1=Gabriel |title=Braves win as Ian Anderson outpitches Gerrit Cole in MLB debut |url=https://www.ajc.com/sports/atlanta-braves/ian-anderson-outpitches-gerrit-cole-in-mlb-debut/JGVVGGGN6JCLDHFECXF5JCZUIY/ |access-date=August 26, 2020 |work=Atlanta Journal Constitution |date=August 26, 2020 |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301140608/https://www.ajc.com/sports/atlanta-braves/ian-anderson-outpitches-gerrit-cole-in-mlb-debut/JGVVGGGN6JCLDHFECXF5JCZUIY/ }}</ref>

整年他拿下3勝2敗，防禦率僅1.95。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=anders000ian|title=Ian Anderson Minor Leagues Statistics & History|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306131853/https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=anders000ian}}</ref>他的主要球種有快速球、變速球、曲球以及少量的伸卡球。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.brooksbaseball.net/landing.php?666120|title=BrooksBaseball.net Player Card: Ian Anderson|website=www.brooksbaseball.net}}</ref>

這年勇士隊成功闖進季後賽，他在面對紅人隊奪勝，讓勇士隊闖進第二輪。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sportstalkatl.com/braves-ian-anderson-makes-history-as-braves-win-first-playoff-series-since-2001/|title=Braves: Ian Anderson makes history as Braves win first playoff series since 2001|first=Chase|last=Irle|date=October 1, 2020|website=SportsTalkATL.com|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2021-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428093751/https://www.sportstalkatl.com/braves-ian-anderson-makes-history-as-braves-win-first-playoff-series-since-2001/}}</ref>後來他在分區賽面對馬林魚再拿一勝，不過後來勇士在國聯冠軍賽輸給道奇。
